Balance Review
==============

The balance review looks at an area from a balance point of view. Things
to consider are the amount and quality of loot in the area, the strengths
of the monsters relative to the reward, difficulty of puzzles etc. Anything
that affects the players and is not cosmetic is covered under balance.

The reviewer needs to consider how hard it is to get the rewards in the
area, and also the effect of the rewards on the game once they are gotten.
Generally, more valuable loot should be harder to get, but even the most
difficult areas should not have items so powerful that they give a player
godlike powers. Conversely, an area should have enough reward that there
is an incentive for players to adventure there. Finally, it should be
recognized that information spreads quite easily, and that once a player
knows how to solve a puzzle, that puzzle is no longer so difficult.

